				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-Cao-M%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%A1c-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-x%C3%A3-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-qu%E1%BA%ADn-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n/poem-OHMF-SMTUy8SSs3daJWY0Q">Chân Định huyện, Cao Mại tổng, Bác Trạch xã Phạm quận công bi văn - 真定縣高邁總博澤社范郡公碑文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/Chi%E1%BA%BFn-tai-ca/poem-cWyDV6yu4wHtFHa_yuOCfw">Chiến tai ca - 戰哉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ch%E1%BB%A7ng-oa-c%E1%BB%B1/poem-OmZprMrp6Q98cV47zLioSA">Chủng oa cự - 種萵苣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-1WwuWOOTnqta5CuA9yU9AQ">Hạ vũ - 賀雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Hung-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-9l2KKaVBxta5Y-v_IMOuog">Hung trạch - 凶宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/Long-H%E1%BB%93-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh/poem-pbmLUR7-RVDz8uEJR8krvw">Long Hồ ngoạ bệnh - 龍湖臥病</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/author-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Nguyễn Cư Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Mao-kh%C3%A2u-3/poem-816JJmH1ANKAym6VLMPV8Q">Mao khâu 3 - 旄丘 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%B9-Bi-t%C3%A2y-nam-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-fAd4MSmwt6gK0B7VvxL7yg">Mỹ Bi tây nam đài - 渼陂西南臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/La-%E1%BA%A8n/Thu%E1%BB%B7-bi%C3%AAn-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-Xm8_cNsdb5SVo-7a8oTaPA">Thuỷ biên ngẫu đề - 水邊偶題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/La-%E1%BA%A8n/author-n_6MEk2_Xxnin0yOJLakrA">La Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-C%E1%BB%A7ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-RzdMkOZO7PJsYJyRM9_PhQ">Vịnh liễu - 詠柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-C%E1%BB%A7ng/author-fHbHbfl-NH8NLQqLmIcmbQ">Tăng Củng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
